name: SpookyHalloweenFloki
description: Welcome to Spooky Halloween Floki! The scariest project living (or dead) on the bsc network. Come for the tricks and stay for the treats. From low taxes to NFTs we’ve got utilities so good, they’re to die for! The haunting begins on October 1st so join us for this spooky holiday season. Our first round of utilities will include 500 NFT's. These NFT's can be staked via our ecosystem to earn Santa Floki tokens. They will have additional use in the Santaverse which will release next year. Holding a Spooky Halloween Floki NFT will also allow you to play Santa Floki’s own P2E game, Santa Floki Rush. In addition The NFT's can be used in The Santaverse to purchase land in prime locations at a discount price of Santa Floki. Also those NFT's will give you entry on to the SantaVerse.
